同你見面<br />\n至於香港班葡萄撚同垃圾泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇用啦 條友都入唔到體制入面<br />\n係海外建立香港流亡政府啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個知將來會發生d 咩事？<br />\n但現代世界你要同當地政府對抗，冇外國既支持根本冇可能成功<br />\n外面唔識人，只識係國內屌鳩人地係出面既冇用做唔野，但反睇自己除左屌人同自戀之外，就冇任何作為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75203bdc02ac16cd1ef5125afc6f89f762f50ad","tid":113360,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"話事話自稱 中共/美國上賓 個位呢 ?"},{"pid":"c58196ac93c28c3122ac30e25a233ab0255b3949","tid":113360,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢條友係外國政圈愈黎愈有名，人地肯同你見面<br />\n至於香港班葡萄撚同垃圾泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華文傳媒戀童癖, 日日舖天蓋地造神<br />\n外國傳媒就首先引述華文媒, <br />\n到外國傳媒直接派人黎, 都係必定訪問佢<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係佢神既原因<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 佢D垃圾英文, 英國佬聽得明, 佢又聽得明?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同外國政治結交語言不通根本唔係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文好又點？政治籌碼就會高d?"},{"pid":"4195b04da9a83367fb59bbfcd91d6c8da9a59deb","tid":113360,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等睇 send e-mail  同屌鳩做</blockquote><br />\n其實如果佢見多幾次前港督，實際作用係咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁日日響網民淨係屌人鳩做果班又有乜嘢貢獻?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff12f464662c6c957101d7b83f2117d17772f38","tid":113360,"uid":51826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"唔通好似濕鳩梁天琦咁咩"},{"pid":"94e800d4c6d5f87c87e86e8305736a505c3b15dd","tid":113360,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor